        <updateDate>2008-06-09T18:59:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Creating Opportunities to Motivate Mass-transit Utilization to Encourage Ridership Act of 2008 or the Commuter Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow employers a refundable tax credit for 50% of the cost of transit passes provided on a tax-free basis to employees. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
